Would you like to maximize your brain's processing speed with brain training that expands your peripheral vision?

Improving your peripheral vision is important for speed reading, judgment, memory and concentration!

This app is a free peripheral vision training app that uses the most simple and effective "Schulte table" to improve peripheral vision.


◆◇ What's Schulte Table?

A table in which numbers from 1 to 25 are arranged randomly in a 5x5 square.

It is one of the brain training techniques that appear in the best-selling "Spy School: Are You Sharp Enough to Be a KGB Agent?", a book filled with know-how to improve the memory of intelligence agents whose brains are their weapons.

By fixing your attention on the center of the table, using only your peripheral vision, and repeating the training of finding numbers in order starting from 1, you can train the peripheral vision, attention, concentration, and self-control necessary for memory.

It was originally devised by German psychiatrist and psychotherapist Walter Schulte as a diagnostic test to study attentional characteristics.


◆◇ Improving your peripheral vision is a shortcut to improving your skills!

Improving peripheral vision, which is the ability to see a wide range, is essential for efficient skill improvement.

It is said that 80% of the information that we humans receive from the outside world is handled by our eyes.

Information obtained from the eyes is sent to the brain, where it is recognized (memory, learning, thinking, judgment) and executed (motor control, etc.).

On the other hand, even if it is in the field of view, there are many things that are not recognized.

It goes without saying that a lot of information is required for correct execution.

Without enough information, you can't make the right decisions.

In other words, for quick and accurate execution, it is important to be able to obtain a lot of information from peripheral vision without wasting visual field information, and improving peripheral vision is a shortcut to skill improvement.


◆◇ Recommended for people like this

◆ Those who want to improve speed reading, memory, judgment, and concentration

◆ Those who want to activate their eyes and brain before studying or working and want to speed up their thinking

◆ An eSports player who mainly plays TPS/FPS where it is important to quickly grasp the position and situation of the enemy

◆ Soccer, basketball, and volleyball players who need to know the positions and movements of their opponents and teammates and make quick decisions.

◆ Tennis and table tennis players whose ability to instantly judge the returned ball and the position of the opponent is important

◆ Athletes of martial arts such as boxing, karate, etc., where the ability to notice the opponent's technique is important

◆ Drivers who need the ability to notice and recognize the movement of dangerous objects such as pedestrians and bicycles around them


With this app, you can enjoy the simple and most effective "Schulte Table" that improves your peripheral vision in 4 modes.

◆ 4 × 4 (16 squares)
◆ 5 × 5 (25 squares)
◆ 6 × 6 (36 squares)
◆ 7 × 7 (49 squares)

Choose a game mode according to your level. Basically, training in 5x5 mode is enough, but if you feel that your concentration, memory, judgment, and speed reading skills are improving, try other modes.

For advanced users, we also have a function that does not erase the tapped number (selectable on the setting screen), so please try it.

Peripheral vision is said to decline with age, but training can not only prevent it, but can also improve it.

3 minutes a day is fine, so please continue training.

If you feel that your peripheral vision has improved, please let us know in the review.

ABOUT MINDDOC

MindDoc is a leading monitoring and self-management app for promoting emotional well-being and coping with such mental illnesses as depression, anxiety, insomnia, and eating disorders.

MindDoc can be used by itself for prevention or self-help, or as a part of treatment with a mental health practitioner.

Our questions, insights, courses, and exercises have been developed by clinical psychologists and are aligned with international treatment guidelines for mental disorders.

As an option, Apple Health data can be linked to the app to detect patterns and relationships between your emotional well-being and mood.

For technical support or other inquiries, please send an email to: feedback@minddoc.de.

 

IMPORTANT INFORMATION

The MindDoc App is a risk class I medical product according to Annex VIII, Rule 11 of the MDR (REGULATION (EU) 2017/745 on medical devices)

Intended Medical Purpose:

The MindDoc monitoring and self-management application medical device provides continuous long-term sign and symptom monitoring of common mental disorders. This protocol is supplemented by courses and exercises. This enables users to recognize patterns in their symptom trajectories which then can be shared with a mental health care provider and used for self-management.

MindDoc thus

provides users orientation regarding the need to consult a mental health care provider by providing an assessment of the general emotional health. A mental health care provider then can include the summary of the protocols in his overall diagnostic and clinical assessment.

enables users to self-manage symptoms and related problems by providing both transdiagnostic and disorder-specific evidence-based courses and exercises which help them to recognize, understand, and cope with signs and symptoms of mental disorders by self-initiating behavior change.

The application explicitly does not replace the diagnosis by a mental health care provider, but can only give orientation on whether to consult a mental health care provider who then can include the results of the medical device in diagnostic processes.

The application explicitly does not replace psychotherapy.

This application consists of three modules: RECORDER, SMART ALARM, STOP SNORING.

RECORDER
Records your talk or snoring while you are asleep (automatic or manual sensitivity level, records only snoring using smart snoring detection), creates the graph of noise in room during the night, takes the total time of snoring down.

SMART ALARM
Helps you wake up easy in your lightest sleep phase and allows you to get up relaxed every morning. Improve your sleep naturally, maximize your sleep efficiency. 

STOP SNORING
Tries to stop your snoring by playing chosen sound or using iPhone vibration when the snoring is detected.

By using the tracker data and by defining your own factors (activities/means/drugs/custom notes) it is possible to find out which facts influence your sleep positively and limit your snoring. At your disposal there are beautiful statistic charts for simple and efficient analyzing of your sleeps/nights.

Snoring detection is based on artificial intelligence (A.I.) with the support of a new Apple machine learning technology. By using a large number of snoring samples, we can achieve high accuracy in statistics and in snoring detection itself.

How to place your device correctly is shown in instructions.
